OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCost of living: One in five
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fexpect to go into debt this
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fyear, survey says          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, One in five people think they will end 
OL,6, up in debt this year and won't be able 
OL,7, to pay it back, a survey has found.    
OL,9,FWith energy bills and council tax set  
OL,10,Fto rise from April, debt charity       
OL,11,FStepChange found 42% of people think   
OL,12,Fthey will struggle to pay these bills. 
OL,14,FIt is urging the Chancellor Rishi Sunak
OL,15,Fto use this week's Spring Statement to 
OL,16,Fdo more to help poorer households.     
OL,18,FMr Sunak told the BBC he cannot "fully 
OL,19,Fprotect" people from the consequences  
OL,20,Fof rising prices.                      
